QuestData.Title: Work Order: Dominance Offensive II
QuestData.Description: Once your red blossom leeks are ready to be picked, you'll need only to package them for pick-up.$b$bJust think; your red blossom leeks will be a part of your faction's efforts in Pandaria!
QuestData.LogDescription: Harvest 8 Ripe Red Blossom Leek plants and provide 40 Red Blossom Leeks for the Dominance Offensive.
